race.comment: ALSTON (5) is an honest type rarely out of the money, scoring at this track (16.55) last time and making it two straight wins. Is yet to taste defeat at this course and distance. Has the ability and expected to prove tough to beat again. PARTY STARTED (1) broke a three run winning streak last start when second and beaten 2.5 lengths (16.73) last time at this track. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of four starts. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Leading chance. I'M TOO MESSY (2) beaten last start over the 300m at this track but finished in the minors in a slick 16.78. Smart time latest and looks a key chance on that form. JADED SMILE (7) is a last start winner from this box who must be respected.
